Reasoning: The paper proposes a method for automatic text summarization in the biomedical domain, which involves mapping the text to biomedical concepts using UMLS and using itemset mining to extract essential subtopics. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Databases (cs.DB).
